	  <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> All bookings have to be made at least 5 hrs in advance for proper facilitation of the service. A successful booking alone does not qualify for a service confirmation. Each booking will be followed up with a confirmation call or SMS to your registered mobile number depending on availability of drivers and proximity of reporting location.</p>
     	  <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> All our drivers are under contractual agreement with the company not to solicit our customers directly or indirectly for any driver services. Also our customers are obligated not to employ any drivers of Driver-Lo on permanent or temporary basis without the consent of the company.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> Any cancellation of a booking by the customer has to be made 2 hours prior to the start of the booking. Otherwise a cancellation charge of Rs. 100/- will be applicable.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> Rates quoted are only indicative and are not binding on the company.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> Please do not insist and/or encourage the driver for over speeding, jumping traffic signals, driving in wrong lane/side, overtaking, offroading, race/competition etc.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> We strictly recommend NOT to leave any cash, valuables, precious items like laptops, mobiles, wallets, handbags, luggage etc in the vehicle and/or in possession of the drivers.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> Driver-Lo or any driver engaged through it will NOT be responsible for any loss, theft or damage.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> Please insist the driver to display the company duty slip(CSR GROUP SERVICES) every time the driver reports for your booking. </p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> In case you have any suspicion or doubt you should always call the DriveR-Lo call center number to report and/or clarify.</p>
          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> We accept payments ONLY in cash and should be made by the customer directly to the driver at the end of the booking.</p>
