          <p class="story_text text-left"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags padding-right-10"></span> You should engage Driver-Lo services ONLY if your vehicle is covered under a comprehensive insurance through a credible motor vehicle insurer in India as Driver-Lo or its driver would not be a party, convict or witness to any legal proceedings held by any court of Law due to such incidents, loss or thefts.</p>
